children.name: A semi-fondant cake that comes in any flavor and can be made with vanilla or chocolate bread and cream. It weighs at least 4 kilograms and is hand-delivered in a cardboard box. The cake's semi-fondant covering provides a smooth, elegant finish while allowing for more flexibility and a lighter texture compared to full fondant. This makes it an ideal choice for a variety of occasions, from birthdays and anniversaries to weddings and corporate events.
